OVERVIEW

  This is an alternative version of Camlp4 distributed separately from
  ocaml. Started from an old version of camlp4 and upgraded to make it
  work with modern ocaml compilers.

  The current version is 1.0.

  Compatible with ocaml versions :
    3.08.1, 3.08.3, 3.08.4, 3.09.0, 3.09.1, 3.09.2, 3.09.3, 3.10.

INSTALL

  Read the file INSTALL to compile.

DEVELOPPERS

  The file DEVEL gives information for people who want to make changes
  in camlp4, or who are just curious.

PROBLEMS

  If you have problems to compile your source files with this version of
  Camlp4, the reason may be that there the new type 'location' is now
  abstract. Consider looking at the file UPGRADING.
